# Rammer Tech -- Brand Color Palette

## Origin

All brand colors are extracted from the Rammer Tech logo (`public/Rammer Tech LOGO.png`).
The logo features a ram silhouette with a crimson gradient (hue ~25 oklch):
bright red (horn) -> deep maroon (body) -> near-black (shadows).

